		<Backstory>Morech is a shadow of ambiguous morality.  He seeks knowledge of creation, destruction, restoration, and decay.  He cares little for either means or ends, but only for knowledge gained thereby.  Life, to him, is merely a spectrum of states of being through which to pass.  From the time of his creation he has kept aloof from other shadows, and more recently that distance has been encouraged by leaders among the shadow community as they fear that he will taint their image.
		
That said, Morech has recently begun to back away from certain magical pursuits that some would describe as 'dark' or 'evil', as he has found that they tend to have unintended and frequently undesirable side effects.</Backstory>

